@AdminCoreApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5005

### Test - Get All Users
GET {{AdminCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/Users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Test - Get Resumen General
GET {{AdminCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/Analytics/resumen-general
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Test - Get Restaurantes Analytics
GET {{AdminCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/Analytics/restaurantes
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Test - Get Tendencias
GET {{AdminCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/Analytics/tendencias
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Test - Get All Roles
GET {{AdminCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/Roles
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Test - Create Rol
POST {{AdminCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/Roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "nombre": "nuevo_rol",
  "descripcion": "Descripción del nuevo rol"
}

### Test - Delete User
DELETE {{AdminCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/Users/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Test - Delete Reserva
DELETE {{AdminCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/Reservas/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
